THE PBC_sig LIBARY

The PBC_sig library is a C library providing implementations of various
signature schemes:

Boneh-Boyen signatures
Boneh-Boyen-Shacham group signatures
Boneh-Lynn-Shacham signatures
Cha-Cheon identity-based signatures

PBC_sig requires the PBC library:

    http://crypto.stanford.edu/pbc/

